    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 with medium model influence. CFD hemolysis predictions satisfy RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all five operating points. Validation against FDA generic pump benchmark demonstrates sufficient model credibility for the intended use of identifying worst-case hemolysis conditions. Assurance level assessed as High based on comprehensive factor coverage, GCI confirmation, and multi-point experimental agreement. The assessment team notes that the sensitivity sweep validation activity (VR-002) provides high-confidence worst-case identification through parametric coverage; the narrative validation rationale is considered sufficient to support the High assurance declaration.",
